our convenience a kaiser mobile clinic is on campus tuesdays and thursdays that provides a wide range of primary care services to find the location and set up an appointment go to http my kp org ca stanforduniversity or call 800 464 4000 hmo name group number kaiser permanente northern california 7145 kaiser permanente southern california 230178 blue shield epo blue shield group 976109 the blue shield epo requires you to see a blue shield provider when you access care the network of providers for the epo plan is the same as that for the ppo and high deductible plans blue shield ppo blue shield group 170292 the blue shield ppo plan allows you the freedom to go to any network provider or to the provider of your choice outside the network while the choice is yours each time you need care your out of pocket costs are substantially lower and more predictable when you go to a blue shield network provider blue shield high deductible ppo blue shield group 170293 the high deductible ppo plan works the same as the blue shield ppo plan but with a much larger out of pocket deductible there are no copayments with this plan instead all benefits including prescription drugs are covered after you meet your deductible what you pay when you see your doctor or get a prescription may be less than you think here are some examples of out of pocket costs with the high deductible ppo plan this plan qualifies for a personal h ealth savings account hsa which allows you to put money aside on a tax deductible basis to pay for medical expenses compare medical plans planning tools learn more about health savings accounts quick links selecting a medical plan compare medical plans planning tools learn about coverage in retirement find out about eligibility cobra hipaa resources plan summaries plan costs prescription drug mail order forms & claim forms hmo faq epo faq blue shield ppo faq blue shield high deductible ppo faq blue shield coverage when traveling contacts blue shield of california www b